title: New Creator: Naomi & Mar
body:
Name: Naomi & Mar 

Socials -
https://www.youtube.com/naomimar (72K subscribers)
https://www.instagram.com/naomiandmar/


Info - Naomi & Mar is a traveling couple that documents their experiences through VLOGs on YouTube and Instagram. Known for their fun and adventurous content, Naomi & Mar have grown their audience to a Global community. Naomi & Mar have expressed interest in crypto recently and have taken notice to the Rally project. It will allow them and their fans to engage and learn about crypto while engaging in ways like they have never before.   

Use Cases -
Coin distribution - YouTube video / Instagram post 
Holding - Discord exclusive content and chats, group calls, cut scenes from YouTube vlogs 
Transacting - charity, access to podcast, Q&As in live events/chats 

Grant - $1000

A 'yes' approves Naomi & Mar and a $1000 treasury grant
A 'no' denies this prop.
